#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1457
msgid "XR Experiences for Rural Communities"
msgstr "Esperienze XR per le comunità rurali"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1458
msgid "Guiding Real-Life Experiences"
msgstr "Guidare esperienze reali"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1460
msgid ""
"Enriching reality with immersive media insights using Extended Reality (XR) "
"and Artificial Intelligence (AI) to empower rural communities through "
"community-driven XR content."
msgstr ""
"Arricchire la realtà con contenuti immersivi attraverso la Realtà Estesa (XR) "
"e l'Intelligenza Artificiale (AI), valorizzando le comunità rurali tramite "
"contenuti XR creati dalla comunità."

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1463
msgid "Discover How"
msgstr "Scopri come"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1464
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "Scopri di più"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1494
msgid "Understanding the Problem"
msgstr "Comprendere il problema"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1495
msgid "The Challenge in Rural Areas"
msgstr "La sfida nelle aree rurali"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1497
msgid ""
"Many regions rich in cultural heritage face significant hurdles that limit "
"tourism, community involvement, and local opportunities."
msgstr ""
"Molti territori ricchi di patrimonio culturale affrontano ostacoli rilevanti "
"che limitano il turismo, il coinvolgimento della comunità e le opportunità locali."

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1503
msgid "Access Difficulties"
msgstr "Difficoltà di accesso"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1505
msgid ""
"Cultural sites in many rural areas struggle to remain open and accessible. "
"Chronic staff shortages make it hard to keep museums and historical "
"buildings operating, while minimal or deteriorating infrastructure further "
"discourages attendance."
msgstr ""
"I siti culturali di molte aree rurali faticano a restare aperti e accessibili. "
"La cronica carenza di personale rende difficile mantenere operativi musei e "
"edifici storici, mentre infrastrutture scarse o deteriorate scoraggiano "
"ulteriormente le visite."

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1510
msgid "Insufficient Essential Services"
msgstr "Servizi essenziali insufficienti"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1512
msgid ""
"Basic visitor amenities—such as restrooms, seating, shelter, and refreshments"
"—are often missing or in disrepair in village centers. Without these "
"fundamental comforts, tourists are less inclined to stay and explore."
msgstr ""
"I servizi essenziali per i visitatori—come bagni, posti a sedere, ripari e "
"punti ristoro—sono spesso assenti o in cattivo stato nei centri rurali. "
"Senza questi comfort fondamentali, i turisti sono meno propensi a fermarsi ed esplorare."

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1517
msgid "Low Visibility & Weak Regional Identity"
msgstr "Scarsa visibilità e debole identità territoriale"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1519
msgid ""
"These communities frequently lack strong branding or promotional efforts. As "
"a result, the area remains \\"
msgstr ""
"Queste comunità spesso non dispongono di un'identità forte o di adeguate "
"attività promozionali. Di conseguenza, il territorio resta poco conosciuto."

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1524
msgid "Poor Dissemination of Local Information"
msgstr "Scarsa diffusione delle informazioni locali"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1526
msgid ""
"Even when interesting sites exist, details about their history, "
"significance, and practical visiting tips are hard to find. Limited "
"distribution channels and fragmented information hinder awareness of what "
"the territory has to offer."
msgstr ""
"Anche quando esistono siti di interesse, le informazioni sulla loro storia, "
"sul loro valore e sui suggerimenti pratici per visitarli sono difficili da "
"reperire. Canali di diffusione limitati e informazioni frammentate ostacolano "
"la conoscenza di ciò che il territorio ha da offrire."

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1538
msgid "XRTourGuide Platform"
msgstr "Piattaforma XRTourGuide"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1540
msgid ""
"An online platform empowering communities to create and share immersive XR "
"virtual tours, enhancing real-world exploration."
msgstr ""
"Una piattaforma online che consente alle comunità di creare e condividere "
"tour virtuali XR immersivi, arricchendo l'esplorazione del mondo reale."

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1546
msgid "Authoring Platform"
msgstr "Piattaforma di authoring"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1548
msgid ""
"A web-based tool allowing users (citizens, organizations) to easily create "
"XR tours with text, images, audio, and video."
msgstr ""
"Uno strumento web che permette agli utenti (cittadini, associazioni, enti) "
"di creare facilmente tour XR con testi, immagini, audio e video."

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1553
msgid "Mobile Application"
msgstr "Applicazione mobile"

#: xr_tour_guide_public/templates/xr_tour_guide_public/landing_page/landing_page.html:1555
msgid ""
"A multi-platform app for users to discover and experience tours. Point your "
